Package: ldcomparison
Type: Package
Title: Linkage Disequilibrium Decay and Phase Correlation
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Martin Johnsson
Maintainer: Martin Johnsson <sorill@gmail.com>
Description: This package contains functions for calculating linkage disequilibrium
    decay within a population and correlations ("persistency of phase") between
    populations.
    It works with phased data (or with pairwise linkage disequilibrium estimated
    by some other means and imported.
